Example Usage
-------------
  class { 'ssh':
    listenaddress => ['127.0.0.5:8888','127.0.0.6:9999'],
        matchblock    => {
          'User johnybravo' => {
            allowAgentForwarding  => 'yes',
            allowTcpForwarding     => 'yes',
          },
          'Address 192.168.75.0/24'   => {
            permitRootLogin       => 'no',
            allowAgentForwarding  => 'no',
          },
        }
   }


Docs used
